{
  "text": "I'm a painter who spent the last decade building instruments instead of paintings. It boots a salvaged laptop straight into an instrument — no operating system underneath it. It grows out of Aesthetic Computer, where eighteen thousand people have already made sixteen thousand little programs. I want to make computing something you play again. That's what I'd do with Restless Egg.",
